id":30113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:40:47.000Z","msg":"Be Water<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93fb46323442fd8c310b8c9e09ec7217dcdc093b","tid":1683384,"uid":254594,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ee802b655c5e5fe8d5cf0f2463f833050bc63504","tid":1683384,"uid":282587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:39:44.000Z","msg":"今晚明顯係藍絲引人去警署門口聚集再圍捕，唔願承認面對的以後可以再去。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:42:00.000Z","msg":"藍屎引唔引都唔應該去狗屋啦<br />\n仲衰唔夠咩<br />\n太子圍左咁耐最叻就係食左20支酒 但0損傷<br />\n有計既應該係調返轉引狗出黎再應付"},{"pid":"a798eb8b7662f316abdc88451ed39ca5dd040b33","tid":1683384,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:42:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad88fe59274712b47dcb95a04b4d2b25f98e4cd","tid":1683384,"uid":194298,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:44:28.000Z","msg":"今時今日情況有d唔同<br />\n6月8月未敢搞街坊和理非，前線知道要be water<br />\n而家真係全面與民為敵，見人就屌見人就拉<br />\n只要睇你唔順眼就可以武力制服<br />\n全部通例守則通通唔駛跟<br />\n街坊look都未必係免死金牌<br />\n要贏只有全民勇武<br />\n老中青見狗就要伏要屠"},{"pid":"ea37e2c8bc6517f3b890c6f6d8b83971df75e192","tid":1683384,"uid":61235,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:44:41.000Z","msg":"因為次次都冇吸取教訓囉<br />\n之前話唔好臨時吹雞<br />\n今日又中午吹<br />\n樣樣野都話核彈,唔係唔出黎下? <br />\n根本冇721,831呢D都做唔到核彈LV囉<br />\n又話be water,變左打陣地<br />\n不停圍狗局<br />\n明知班藍絲出黎搞事會冇野<br />\n但為啖氣沖埋去<br />\n結果就自己呢邊比人拉晒"},{"pid":"2597ac0a74e6569ab1ad0ba6bd70bc66994ffd9d","tid":1683384,"uid":158504,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"abeb99967639efa5f6973af7331f56bb52ea2d23","tid":1683384,"uid":15129,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:29:47.000Z","msg":"好矛盾<br />\n<br />\n「為啖氣」呢三個字好敏感，發生咗咁多事依然坐係屋企係麻木不仁當手足condom 。但明知重防都要走出去，然後上嚟話人多就無事，係你地唔出去幫手.......<br />\n<br />\n我啖氣都吞唔落，但係咪真係「為啖氣」就硬碰以表示有義氣無放棄手足？我真係唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:46:32.000Z","msg":"你要諗下自己出去有冇用<br />\n今日有無目的 有無行程？<br />\n明知對家set埋局重防 去嚟為咩？<br />\n得罪講，我淨係諗到大家鳩叫口號一晚，Set RB等驅散比人拉<br />\n<br />\n6－8月，記唔記得我哋曾經就呢個問題 同早期班前線嘈過？<br />\n當時個班前線係好心水清<br />\n佢哋話 咁做係要黑狗清場難睇 甚至引佢出醜 盡可能將抗爭規模擴大<br />\n我哋當時接納呢個解釋，所以先次次遊行完會玩RB<br />\n去到今日，你覺得仲需要咁做咩？手頭黑狗核彈已經多到用唔曬<br />\n<br />\n<strong>所以唔係有人做你就要跟住去<br />\n冇意義嘅 唔去唔會有人怪你</strong>"},{"pid":"fb709a942bc1f9401c016aa808bf1340a434a3aa","tid":1683384,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aad2538894319cf0087b06f175a8fa3905d3ed27","tid":1683384,"uid":274336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c9ba2b502d2344b5845f25eb3c3b327ca887015","tid":1683384,"uid":326665,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:22:53.000Z","msg":"而家睇返六，七月啲片發覺真係少左好前線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:32:09.000Z","msg":"2700個唔係純粹數字...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾時先重視呢場仗，大部分人好似玩game咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:46:38.000Z","msg":"比人拉過一次，揹住兩條罪，仲點敢再出黎<br />\n再捉到真係入面困到開庭果日架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95065e6d1a77a990dfc47b1bae91e3ded4f00f5b","tid":1683384,"uid":233909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:49:59.000Z","msg":"到咁耐都玩陣地戰，敵退我進，敵進我退，無散水意思，一散水又比人話散水撚，到比人拉左又咩都做唔倒<br />\n不被捕，不流血 先係王道"},{"pid":"cfc44286ecaafcd78e5a2cdcb33889a2db669424","tid":1683384,"uid":63117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:00:48.000Z","msg":"其實比對家滲透曬帶風向先係致命傷<br />\n有理又唔用腦 一味盲跟 乜鳩po 都幾百正皮你就知幾嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"424e7737922977c8f4f4e01aefc36f9fa606ad52","tid":1683384,"uid":2986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:07:48.000Z","msg":"跟本圍狗屋係送頭 講左好撚耐都係要圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e4f69117856cfb2dfee6bddf9da5c935600e56","tid":1683384,"uid":158504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:42:10.000Z","msg":"檢討post永遠沉底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b977665ff764497580e53d82899301fb6e5e9a0","tid":1683384,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:44:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d84d7632399a7bcc8d7bc7d115b71664072e6e6f","tid":1683384,"uid":101714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:47:26.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a8818596096bb37fc6cae717446f74ea0f0a2111","tid":1683384,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:56:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfdca9741785d171e3e2e97814b80930da41d208","tid":1683384,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11af544f11cf6e656015023139eaff6c03a76284","tid":1683384,"uid":158504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:57:11.000Z","msg":"－ 問定先: 如果解放軍出動，係咪即刻番屋企？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1606038/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1606038/page/1</a><br />\n－ 你出防暴？咁我返屋企訓教了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1424189/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1424189/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"894db9bf7254381041bf8b5c703b6b0b8b2c9741","tid":1683384,"uid":129848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:57:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c80471a2923fba775ab9dc539f9e22bbfe88a562","tid":1683384,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:58:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37be7ca6fe174373c82d3e38d7dc7f46f6421274","tid":1683384,"uid":78060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:58:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a072d501d5dface595138665aa77baec2c4be85e","tid":1683384,"uid":283711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfb946a3e544d7d235ba4a118a5e7d764acb66b3","tid":1683384,"uid":158504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:21:20.000Z","msg":"6月 對家話出解放軍 我哋回應係 返屋企訓覺<br />\n8月 圍狗屋發現中伏 我哋嘅檢討都係 返屋企訓覺<br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得早期612 616嗰陣，我哋不斷強調啲咩？<br />\n<strong>『Be Water，不流血，不受傷，不被捕』</strong><br />\n背後精神就係唔硬碰，因為長期戰有排玩，好似水咁來去自如，唔係對家挑機我就一定要回應，我哋永遠掌握主動權<br />\n<br />\n依家？話人散水撚 話人唔做嘢 話人唔幫現場手足<br />\n氣氛越來越差，幾次行動完咗都冇點檢討改善<br />\n就算有post但都冇人理<br />\n<br />\n隨著越來越多衝突，大家沉迷咗屌狗圍狗，為做而做<br />\n甚至明知重防有伏都要去，完全忘記咗Be Water嘅精神，為啖氣去送頭，甚至唔諗下風險<br />\n7－8月講到依家嘅道理，我發現最近越嚟越嚴重，可能大家香港人善忘DNA發作，集體失憶<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔該大家，真係用下腦，唔係有人吹雞或者一時嬲就要出，諗下有冇伏，做嚟有冇意義先</span></ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家得閒嘅不妨望下3個月前嘅自己<br />\n － 問定先: 如果解放軍出動，係咪即刻番屋企？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1606038/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1606038/page/1</a><br />\n － 你出防暴？咁我返屋企訓教了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1424189/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1424189/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:00:15.000Z","msg":"推!"},{"pid":"9586355c79d939c16d563bdfd7be5dde964f87a1","tid":1683384,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:04:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21297e3b8a4112bb2efc1cf01f748c5ba70699cc","tid":1683384,"uid":59799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:07:05.000Z","msg":"好嬲，想做啲嘢，我明白，唔緊要。<br />\n大家將你嘅怒火發洩係啲唔會打返你嘅嘢度，就算係唔關事嘅都好。<br />\n講咁多即係叫大家見到警察打人，你就裝修；見到有人被自殺，你又裝修。<br />\n將所有嘢推哂落中資店嗰度，唔需要冤有頭債有主咁報仇。"},{"pid":"611b63d006bd72485dd2964cbfe30ce0ba6083b1","tid":1683384,"uid":170199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:07:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"eaaf4f6c1200035e428e052dfee57dc9551abdad","tid":1683384,"uid":173072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:07:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">無地鐵點be water 呀</span></span><br />\n呢招破左, 出第二招啦"},{"pid":"0bd71533d4e39bd9fc94fffb8b179133ff5f2b13","tid":1683384,"uid":59799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:08:38.000Z","msg":"反正你圍狗又傷唔到佢，咁不如針對啲你傷害到嘅嘢仲直接"},{"pid":"c5c576c0553950838d02a9e1203be4042edf5ea1","tid":1683384,"uid":97979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:10:39.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n任何時候要保持獨立思考<br />\n唔好為啖氣送頭"},{"pid":"ec12d34b1cb3097c8ff76b8bd6bfec2352a9bd4b","tid":1683384,"uid":263806,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"1c9ba2